    A data tracker for spatial data. It sends change data to whoever is listening (usually a WidgetGUI or Widget understanding SpaceData messages). Messages consist in a time stamp and a list of changes to the previous state of the space (deletion/creation/move of points and lines).

    The metadata are the space properties, namely:

    • type (SpaceType),
    • edgeEffects (EdgeEffects),
    • precision (double),
    • units (String),

    plus the descendant-specific properties:

    • for FlatSurface:
      • x-limits (Interval) and
      • y-limits (Interval)
    • for SquareGrid:
      • cellSize(double),
      • x-nCells (int),
      • y-nCells (int) (optional, if absent = x-nCells)

    This DataTracker is not instantiated by a DataTrackerNode, but by the SpaceNode it points to.
